questionString: Return a tennis player after the tennis player "Gvidas Sabeckis" which has the second most height?
questionStringTagged:
Return tennis player after the tennis player "Gvidas Sabeckis" which has the second most

height

?
query:
SELECT ?Seed WHERE 
{
     ?Seed rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/TennisPlayer>. 
     <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gvidas_Sabeckis> rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/TennisPlayer>. 
     <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gvidas_Sabeckis> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/height> ?NN. 
     ?Seed <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/height> ?n. FILTER (?n<?NN)
} 
ORDER BY DESC(?n)
LIMIT 1
OFFSET 1
